      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I see the missing delete now, that definitely explains one part of it. But even after fixing that in the telemetry class, we're still seeing these weird, unexplained dips in available memory in other modules that look totally clean. \n\nIt's like the leak is just hiding in the background or popping up in places we aren't even looking at. How do I actually track down something that's being that elusive in a real-time system where I don't have the luxury of Valgrind or a heavy debugger?",
